        "created_at": "2019-01-28T02:53:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Found for $6.99.<br>\nTranslucent ruby.<br>\nAromas of crushed red fruits.<br>\nLight-medium bodied, a slightly \u2018dusty\u2019 element, a shot of bright and crisp acidity, but just a tad short of being a \u2018medium finish\u2019.<br>\nIt steers away from \u2018tasting cheap\u2019, but it\u2019s certainly not serious\u2026Just a gulpable, bistro addition.<br>\n85 pts.</p>",
