        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"149471\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Dubeouf accounts for around a quarter of the entire production of Beaujolais, and many small farmers depend on them as a market for their grapes, so it\u2019s in everyone\u2019s interests that they succeed. I get the sense that the wine making may soon evolve in a more exciting direction.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I buy one bottle a year on Beaujolais Nouveau Day (it\u2019s the only option for the new vintage, on that day where I live). I\u2019m doing my part.</p>",
